        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Restricting the Use of Solitary Confinement Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill restricts the use of solitary confinement for inmates in federal custody, including by requiring hearings and other procedures for an inmate to contest placement in solitary confinement.</p>]]></text>
